  "prompt": "How do I contact Handy customer service?",
  "response": "To contact Handy customer service, you can try the following methods:\n\n1. **Website**: Visit Handy's official website and navigate to the \"Help\" or \"Support\" section. There, you may find a variety of FAQs that could address your concerns.\n\n2. **Email**: You can send an email to Handy's customer service at support@handy.com. Be sure to include detailed information about your issue for a quicker response.\n\n3. **Phone**: Handy may provide a customer service phone number on their website. It's worth checking there for the most accurate and up-to-date contact number.\n\n4. **App**: If you have the Handy app, you can also reach customer service through the app\u2019s support features. \n\n5. **Social Media**: Handy is active on platforms like Twitter and Facebook. You can send them a message or look for their official account to get assistance.\n\nMake sure to have any relevant details handy, such as your account information or specifics about your service request, to help expedite the process.",
